        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThere were four TODO comments in the ControlLoopEventManager class that showed up as technical debt. They were comments on locking and on checking if the event manager was active. As locking is so tricky, I thought it best to leave those TODO comments there for now and address them if locking was being revisited in the future.",
